column5: Hi everyone heading up for my first trip of the season to Virginia Beach on Lake Simcoe this Wednesday in the am, if anyone is interested in meeting up give me a pm thx! Gona be taking out my 2 man clam....
would like to join you but i will only slow you down drastically.  not only that but i have an appointment to see the orthopedic doctor about my fracture.  good luck.  todd
